nhc_headline: ...KIKO BECOMES A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY...
summary: ...KIKO BECOMES A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY... As of 5:00 AM HST Wed Sep 10 the center of Kiko was located near 22.9, -158.1 with movement W at 12 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
